articles.author: Chloe Peterson
articles.title: 'It was pretty egregious': Indiana Fever's Steph White on 'disrespectful' officiating - IndyStar
articles.description: Stephanie White thought there were 3 incorrect calls in the final 36 seconds of the Indiana Fever's 2-point loss vs New York on Saturday.
articles.content:
• A no-call on the Indiana Fever's Caitlin Clark sends team to 90-88 loss to New York
